result.name: Arena Bar by Zerve

reviews.text:
Cool location to hang out and have some drinks on weekends.
One star is missing from my side because I think they are quite high priced and I don´t really see a reason for that. The other is missing because I can´t understand why you have like 4 tables to play beer pong, but only one or two can be used at the same time... It´s annoying to wait for one hour until you´re allowed to play one game but in fact there are 3 more free tables to play at the same time...

one of a kind experience. best bar in Hong Kong i would say. all the staffs are super friendly, they are like friends to me. it is not the flashy type of bar, but if you want somewhere that has a great vibe, chill and just enjoy your time, this is the place to go.

came here because of the great reviews, but was very disappointed. firstly, the staff were super rude - they got mad whenever we asked to play a game (???). secondly, we ordered whiskey sodas for pong and it was literally 1% whiskey. finally, they restrict ur game to 10 mins and tell u to gtfo after..... save ur cash and go play beer pong at joe's
Commercial beerpong place. Overcrowded and not enjoyable.
A great place for football. A small zone for people who don't smoke would be great for non - smoker.
